profile:
All our painters are CCQ-certified and our company is RBQ-certified, which means we have high-quality standards and we are allowed to execute painting contracts on commercial, industrial and residential buildings everywhere in the province of Quebec, and we do so in the appropriate level of effort.

Our company’s constant growth is an evidence of the quality the services we offer. This prosperity allowed us to invest in state-of-the-art equipment, which allowed us to be very productive and to offer results of exceptional quality. Moreover, we never neglect safety and cleanliness.

Our technical expertise, our 22 years of experience, our attention to detail and our desire to go beyond our clients’ expectations make us experts and help us be a choice reference for your paint projects.
